<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="30">
    <title>503 — Mantenimiento</title>
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #F0F4F8; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; color: #0D3B66; }
        .box { text-align: center; max-width: 480px; padding: 2rem; }
        .icon { font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .code { font-size: 5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #d1dde8; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
        h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
        p { color: #5a7fa8; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: .9375rem; }
        .badge { display: inline-block; background: #fff3cd; color: #92400e; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 20px; padding: .3rem .9rem; font-size: .8125rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .refresh { font-size: .8125rem; color: #a0b4c8; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="box">
        <div class="code">503</div>
        <span class="badge">En mantenimiento</span>
        <h1>Volveremos pronto</h1>
        <p>El sistema está en mantenimiento programado.<br>Esta página se actualizará automáticamente.</p>
        <p class="refresh">Actualizando en 30 segundos…</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>